Class HttpMethodsServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • org.eclipse.jetty.tests.webapp.HttpMethodsServlet

  • public class HttpMethodsServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
    Servlet declaring the various do* methods. The Jetty internals for OPTIONS should detect the declared do* methods and return an appropriate listing of available OPTIONS on an OPTIONS request.
